opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 27th day of October, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and the Petition for an Immediate Hearing are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
